transcript:
Agent: Hello, is this Mr. Johnson?
Customer: Yes, it is. Who's calling?
Agent: My name is Emily, and I'm calling from GreenTech Solutions. We specialize in energy-efficient lighting systems.
Customer: Okay, I've heard of you. What can you do for me?
Agent: We've recently launched a new line of LED bulbs that can help reduce your energy consumption by up to 50%.
Customer: That sounds interesting. I've been looking to cut down my electricity bills.
Agent: Exactly. Our bulbs are not only energy-efficient but also have a longer lifespan compared to traditional bulbs.
Customer: How much do they cost?
Agent: We're currently offering a discount for first-time customers. You can get a pack of 10 bulbs for $50.
Customer: That's not bad. But I'd like to know more about the warranty and customer support.
Agent: Absolutely. Our products come with a 5-year warranty, and our customer support team is available 24/7.
Customer: Okay, that sounds good. Can you send me a quote and some more information about the product?
Agent: I'd be happy to. I'll send you an email with all the details. Would you like me to follow up with you next week?
Customer: Yes, that would be great. Thank you, Emily.
Agent: You're welcome, Mr. Johnson. I'll talk to you soon.
Customer: Looking forward to it. Bye.
Agent: Bye, have a great day.
